{"tid":2067302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港商家要比錢了！人行將在港發行100億人民幣央票！","createTime":"2020-06-17T01:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T03:39:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcd0552e8e6f02138e57e982089aa74e9b696a1","tid":2067302,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532521-20200617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532521-20200617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=98069ed2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532521-20200617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=49ca74e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532521-20200617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n人民銀行公布，將通過金管局債務工具中央結算系統(CMU)，招標發行今年第6期中央銀行票據，規模100億元人民幣，期限6個月，起息日本月29日，到期日為今年12月28日。<br />\n<br />\n人行指，發行央票為豐富香港高信用等級人民幣金融產品，完善香港人民幣收益率曲線。"},{"pid":"039e4279930715dd4ee029b4e2496c7a2c4d4475","tid":2067302,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"當香港富豪係提款機！回血劍！"},{"pid":"e5b402c76d6109780c7c0a8b1a24017063654c7b","tid":2067302,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:49:33.000Z","msg":"軍票"},{"pid":"eff20ea6ebb83ad0b450a61d3a3a4589faf57e56","tid":2067302,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:50:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"79774515db8df8a047c3b8a48fb2cc07fda4605a","tid":2067302,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"青海省國資委控股的青海省投，有一筆明年到期的3億美元債未能付息，令另外兩筆債券交叉違約。及後，白武士出現，一間名為國臻國際的聲稱第三方公司向債券持有人（債主）提出以41折及36折收購，該債券利率為6.4%，債主息後都輸入肉之餘，還發現該白武士原來是青海省國資委背景，即是自己人明cap水，債主們於上星期登報及派傳單抗議，又去信證監會投訴，最新消息加碼至63折及59折，開天索價落地還錢的談判策略，應該有不少苦主落叠。"},{"pid